                    <item name="UserText" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Assign bricks to the column so damage severity forms a clear vertical gradient with high polarity between the start and end.

Top region must use the most damaged bricks available in the set.
Bottom region must use only bricks with zero or only little damages.

Between top and bottom, choose bricks so that severity decreases smoothly with height.</item>
